{
  "title": "OpenSearch Cluster",
  "uid": "opensearch-cluster",
  "tags": ["opensearch", "rcs-etcd"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "10s",
  "time": { "from": "now-30m", "to": "now" },
  "templating": { "list": [] },
  "annotations": { "list": [] },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Async fetch rate (success vs failure)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "rate(stepflow_async_fetch_success_count_total[1m])", "legendFormat": "success/s", "refId": "A" },
        { "expr": "rate(stepflow_async_fetch_failure_count_total[1m])", "legendFormat": "failure/s", "refId": "B" }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops",
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10 }
        }
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Cumulative async fetches (success)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [{ "expr": "stepflow_async_fetch_success_count_total", "refId": "A" }],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short" } },
      "options": { "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area" }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Cumulative async fetches (failure)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [{ "expr": "stepflow_async_fetch_failure_count_total", "refId": "A" }],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            { "color": "green", "value": null },
            { "color": "red", "value": 1 }
          ]}
        }
      },
      "options": { "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area" }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Deferred coverage",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 14 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Pending OpenSearch SPI coverage**\n\nThe upstream `_cluster/health`, node-level heap and CPU, indexing-rate, and cluster-state-version metrics are not yet emitted via the OpenSearch telemetry SPI in 3.0.0. They will populate here as core OpenSearch instruments those paths.\n\n**Pending histogram support**\n\nThe rcs-etcd plugin emits `rcs_etcd.blob.{write,read,list}.duration` as exponential histograms. The bundled stepflow-o11y OpenTelemetry Collector contrib (v0.95.0) Prometheus exporter does not currently surface exponential histograms to the scrape endpoint. Counters are unaffected and visible on the rcs-etcd Plugin dashboard."
      }
    }
  ]
}
